data.name: Joker, the Unknowable
data.notes: "Joker, the Unknowable" is inside the top of the giant plant at Divine Roost at the northern tip of Noctilum along with 19 level 60 Blatta friends. They are a great source for quickly levelling up party members, levelling Classes and stocking up on Tatty Insect Wings to create Insectoid Slayer Augments.
